title: Juego 2048 - Jugar 2048 en línea

title: Play Double 2048 2048 Game
snippet: How to play: Use your arrow keys to move the tiles. When two tiles with the same number touch, they merge into one! Tip: Press and hold H to view information about each tile. Join the numbers and get to the 2048 tile! Careful: this game is extremely addictive!
